Vine.js
-About 1.6KB
-Can be used with or without the DOM

Tested in:(I'll set up some test pages soon to test in other browsers)
-Chrome 11

API:

vine.bind(target:Object/DOMElement,type:String,handler:Function) //binds a handler to the element
vine.unbind(target:Object/DOMElement[,type:String][,handler:Function)) //unbinds a handler based on criteria
vine.trigger(target:Object/DOMElement[,type:String][,event:Object/Event]) //returns event object after handler execution

vine.Event(event:Object/Event) //normalizes an event (internal)